<D>__{don't shoot me, don't shoot me, i have what you want. i have what you want. i can get us out of the country tonight. tonight. no passport. fly out. tonight...oh god, don't shoot me! i swear on my mother. look at me: am i lying to you? a sea plane. tonight. help me. i swear to you.}
